*libvorbis-1.1.1 (16 Sep 2005)

  16 Sep 2005; Brandon Low <lostlogic@gentoo.org> +libvorbis-1.1.1.ebuild:
  Bump up to the latest release from xiph.org, this includes the latest of
  aotuv's patches, so there is no need for patching (yay). Unstable in all
  arches, especially needs testing in ppc-macos, because I dunno if I did the
  symlink stuff right.

